(4, 'TAKWA', 'takwa', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">الْحَمْدُ للهِ الَّذِي أَظْهَرَ قُدْرَتَهُ عَلَى خَلْقِهِ\r\nبِإِظْهَارِ عَبْدِهِ وَحَبِيبِهِ وَرَسُوْلِهِ، سَيِّدِنَا مُحَمَّدٍ ﷺ بإِذْنِهِ،\r\nأَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ،وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ،\r\nاللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ وَسَلَّمْ وَبَارِكْ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ الْهَادِي إِلَى صِرَاطِكَ الْمُسْتَقِيمِ،\r\nوَعَلَى آلِهِ وَصَحْبِهِ وَالْمُجَاهِدِيْنَ فِي سَبِيْلِكَ القَوِيمِ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>.<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><br></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">أَمَّا بَعْدُ، فَيَا عِبَادَ اللَّهِ، اِتَّقُوا اللَّهَ الَّذِي\r\nلَا إِلَهَ سِوَاهُ، أَعُوْذُ بِاللَّهِ مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ الرَّحِيمِ، يَا أَيُّهَا\r\nالَّذِينَ آمَنُوا اتَّقُوا اللَّهَ وَلْتَنْظُرْ نَفْسٌ مَا قَدَّمَتْ لِغَدٍ وَاتَّقُوا\r\nاللهَ إِنَّ اللَّهَ خَبِيرٌ بِمَا تَعْمَلُوْنَ</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><br></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Ma’asyiral Hadirin Jama’ah Jum’at Rahimakumullah<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; text-indent: 1cm;\">Marilah kita tingkatkan ketakwaan kita kepada Allah SWT,\r\nagar kita selalu mendapatkan jalan keluar dalam setiap menghadapi kesulitan.\r\nSebagaimana firman Allah di dalam surat Ath-Thalaq ayat [2-3]:</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; text-indent: 1cm;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">}</span></b><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">وَمَنْ يَّتَّقِ اللّٰهَ يَجْعَلْ لَّهٗ مَخْرَجًاۙ ۝٢</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span> </span></b><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">وَّيَرْزُقْهُ مِنْ حَيْثُ لَا يَحْتَسِبُۗ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>{<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 1cm; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">“Barangsiapa bertakwa kepada Allah, maka Allah akan\r\nmemberikan kepadanya jalan keluar dan akan memberikan rezeki kepadanya diluar\r\nperhitungan dan tanpa di duga-duga sebelumnya.”</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">[QS. Ath- Thalaq ayat :2-3]<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><br></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Ma’asyiral Hadirin Jama’ah Jum’at Rahimakumullah<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Taqwallah, pada dasarnya, di dalam kitab kifayatul\r\natqiya’ disebutkan:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">التَّقْوَى وَهِي عِبَارَةٌ عَنِ اِمْتِثَالِ أَوَامِرِ اللهِ\r\nوَاجْتِنَابِ نَوَاهِيِهِ ظَاهِرًا وَبَاطِنًا مَعَ اِسْتِشْعَارِ التَّعْظِيمِ اللهَ</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><br></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">“</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">taqwa adalah </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Menjalankan\r\nsemua perintah perintah allah dan menjauhi semua larangan-larangan allah lahir\r\nmaupun batin beserta niat untuk mengagunggkan allah swt</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">”</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Sikap dan perilaku taqwallah seperti di atas, tentu saja\r\ndidorong oleh keimanan dan keyakinan atas kebenaran adanya perintah dan\r\nlarangan itu dari allah, Dan sekaligus mengimani dan meyakini akan adanya jaza’\r\natau pembalasan di hari kiamat nanti. Untuk meningkatkan taqwallah, marilah\r\nkita renungkan perbincangan rasulullah dengan para sahabatnya. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Pada waktu itu Rasulullah duduk di kerumuni sejumlah\r\nsahabatnya, beliau mengatakan; “siapa di antara kalian yang mau menerima\r\npesan-pesan dan mengamalkan nya, serta mengajarkan kepada orang lain yang mau\r\nmengamalkan nya.”<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Abu Hurairah yang pada saat itu duduk didekat Rasulullah\r\nmenyahut; “Wahai Rasulullah, saya bersedia menerima dan mengamalkannya, juga\r\nbersedia meneruskan pesan itu kepada orang orang yang mau mengamalkannya.”<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Kemudian Rasulullah menarik tangan Abu Hurairah seraya\r\nbersabda;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"line-height: 150%; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">اتَّقِ\r\nالْمَحَارِمَ تَكُنْ أَعْبَدَ النَّاسِ، وَارْضَ بِمَا قَسَمَ اللهُ لَكَ تَكُنْ أَغْنَى\r\nالنَّاسِ، وَأَحْسِنُ إِلَى جَارِكَ تَكُنْ مُؤْمِنًا، وَأَحِبُّ لِلنَّاسِ كَمَا تُحِبُّ</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><br></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"line-height: 150%; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">“Jauhilah larangan-larangan Allah, pasti engkau akan\r\nmenjadi orang yang paling patuh kepada-Nya. Ridlalah atas rezeki yang telah\r\ndiberikan Allah kepadamu,pasti engkau akan menjadi manusia yang paling kaya.\r\nBerbuat baiklah kepada tetanggamu, niscaya engkau akan menjadi orang yang hidup\r\naman. Berikanlah kesukaan kepada orang lain dengan apa yang engkau sukai, maka\r\nengkau menjadi orang yang selamat. Dan jangan-lah engkau memperbanyak tertawa,\r\nsebab banyak tertawa itu bisa mematikan hati.”(HR&gt; at-Turmudzi)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Ma’asyiral Hadirin Jama’ah Jum’at Rahimakumullah<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"line-height: 150%; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Pesan Rasulullah tersebut, yang pertama adalah agar kita\r\nmenjahui larangan-larangan Allah, agar bisa menjadi orang yang patuh kepadanya.\r\nHal ini dapat di fahami, bahwa menjahui larangan lebih berat daripada\r\nmelaksanakan perintah. Jika kita tidak sanggup menjaga keburukan mustahil dapat\r\nmendatangkan kebaikan. Nabi bersabda:&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"line-height: 150%; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">مَا أَمَرْتُكُمْ\r\nبِهِ فَأْتُوا مِنْهُ مَا اسْتَطَعْتُمْ، وَمَا نَهَيْتُكُمْ عَنْهُ فَاجْتَبُوهُ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>»<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">“Apa saja yang aku perintahkan, lakukanlah menurut\r\nkemampuanmu. Dan apa saja yang aku larang, tinggalkanlah sepenuhnya.”<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"line-height: 150%; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Pesan Rasulullah yang kedua, agar kita bisa dengan rela\r\nmenerima rezeki yang telah diberikan Allah, supaya kita menjadi orang terkaya.\r\nYang berarti tidak mengharapkan bantuan orang lain, tidak cenderung\r\nmenginginkan hal-hal yang bukan milik kita dan bukan bagian kita, dan tidak\r\nmuncul perasaan rendah diri, dan juga tidak selalu menunggu uluran tangan dari\r\norang lain seperti jiwa pengemis. Sebab rezeki akan datang dengan sendirinya\r\ntanpa perlu di kejar-kejar, intinya ikhtiyar sepenuhnya dan bertawakal kepadanya.\r\nRasulullah bersabda:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"line-height: 150%; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">إِنَّ\r\nالرِّزْقَ لَيَطْلُبُ الْعَبْدَ كَمَا يَطْلُبُهُ أَجَلُهُ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>».</span></b><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span> </span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>)</span></b><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">رواه ابن حبان</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>(<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">“Sesungguhnya rezeki itu akan datang kepada seseorang\r\nsebagaiman datangnya ajal kepadanya.” (HR. Ibnu Hibban).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Ma’asyiral Hadirin Jama’ah Jum’at Rahimakumullah<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"line-height: 150%; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Pesan Rasulullah yang ketiga adalah, agar kita bersikap\r\nbaik dengan tetangga, agar supaya menjadi orang yang aman, siapapun tetangga\r\nitu. Rasulullah bersumpah-sumpah:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"line-height: 150%; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">وَالله\r\nلَا يُؤْمِنُ، وَاللَّهِ لَا يُؤْمِنُ، وَاللَّهِ لَايُؤْمِنُ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>.<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Ketika ada yang menanyakan siapa orangnya yang dikatakan\r\ntidak beriman, sampai Rasulullah bersumpah-sumpah seperti itu, Rasulullah\r\nkemudian menjawab:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">الَّذِي لَا يَأْمَنُ جَارُهُ بَوَائِقَهُ». </span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>)</span></b><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">رواه احمد</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>(<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">“Orang yang tetangganya tidak pernah merasa aman dari\r\ngangguannya.”(HR. Imam Ahmad).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Pesan Rasulullah yang ke empat adalah, agar kita\r\nmenghargai hak hak orang lain sebagaimana kita menghargai hak hak kita sendiri.\r\nApabila kita senang diperlakukan baik, maka kita harus berlaku baik kepada\r\norang lain. Apabila kita senang dihormati orang lain, maka hormatilah orang\r\nlain, bila kita mampu berlaku&nbsp; untuk\r\norang lain dengan ukuran diri sendiri, maka kita akan hidup bahagia dan\r\nselamat. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Pesan Rasulullah yang ke lima atau yang terakhir adalah,\r\nagar tidak memperbanyak tertawa terbahak-bahak. Karena hal itu dapat\r\nmenyebabkan hati kita mati, Rasulullah berpesan agar kita selalu menampakkan\r\nwajah yang cerah, berseri-seri, ramah tamah,tampak bahagia akan tetapi tidak\r\ntertawa terbahak-bahak yg dapat mengakibatkan matinya hati.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Ma’asyiral Hadirin Jama’ah Jum’at Rahimakumullah<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Itulah beberapa pesan yang di sampaikan oleh Baginda\r\nRasulullah SAW kepada para sahabat, dan tujuannya tentu juga kepada kita semua\r\nyang menjadi umat Rasulullah SAW. Marilah kita ikuti petunjuk-petunjuk beliau,\r\nagar kita menjadi umat yang baik, yang hidup layak di dunia dan berbahagia di\r\nkehidupan akhirat kelak, Amin Ya Rabbal Alamin.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"line-height: 150%; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">بَارَكَ\r\nاللَّهُ لِي وَلَكُمْ فِي الْقُرْآنِ الْعَظِيمِ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span> </span></b><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">وَنَفَعَنِي وَإِيَّاكُمْ بِمَا فِيْهِ مِنَ الْآيَاتِ وَالذِّكْرِ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span> </span></b><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">الْحَكِيمِ، وَتَقَبَّلَ مِنِّي وَمِنْكُمْ تِلَاوَتَهُ، إِنَّهُ\r\nهُوَ السَّمِيعُ الْعَلِيمُ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>.<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"line-height: 150%; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2025-07-30 14:21:21', '2025-07-30 14:21:21');
INSERT INTO `khutbahs` (`id`, `judul`, `slug`, `image`, `desc`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(5, 'ZUHUD', 'zuhud', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">الْحَمْدُ\r\nلِلَّهِ الَّذِي تُسَبِّحُ لَهُ الرِّمَالُ، وَتَسْجُدُ لَهُ الظلالُ، خَلَقَ الْإِنْسَانَ\r\nمِنَ الطَّيْنِ اللازب وَالصَّلْصَالِ، وَزَيَّنَ صُورَتَهُ بِأَحْسَنِ تَقْوِيمٍ وَأَتَم\r\nاعْتِدَالِ، وَأَذِنَ لَهُ فِي قَرْعِ بَابِ الْخِدْمَةِ بِالْغُدُوِّ وَالْأَصَالِ،\r\nأَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ الَّذِي ضَرَبَ\r\nلَنَا فِي الدُّنْيَا بِأَنْوَاعِ الأَمْثَالِ، وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ\r\nوَرَسُولُهُ الَّذِي أَمَرَنَا بِالزُّهْدِ وَقَصْرِ الْأَمَالِ، وَنَهَانَا عَنِ التَّفَاخُرِ\r\nوَالتَّكَاثُرِ بِالأَمْوَالِ اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَى سَيِّدِنَا مُحَمَّدٍ سَيِّدِ\r\nالْأَنْبِيَاءِ وَعَلَى آلِهِ وَصَحْبِهِ الَّذِينَ كَانُوا فِي الدِّينِ كَأَمْثَالِ\r\nالْجِبَالِ، وَسَلَّمْ تَسْلِيمًا كثيرا<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">أَمَّا\r\nبَعْدُ؛ فَيَا أَيُّهَا الْمُسْلِمُوْنَ، أَتَّقُوا اللَّهَ حَقَّ تُقَاتِهِ، وَلَا\r\nتَمُوتُنَّ إِلَّا وَأَنْتُمْ مُسْلِمُوْنَ، قَالَ تَعَالَى فِي كِتَابِهِ الْكَرِيمِ:\r\nأَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ الرَّحِيمِ، وَاضْرِبْ لَهُمْ مَثَلَ الْحَيُوةِ\r\nالدُّنْيَا كَمَاءِ أَنْزَلْنَاهُ مِنَ السَّمَاءِ فَاخْتَلَطَ بِهِ نَبَاتُ الْأَرْضِ\r\nفَأَصْبَحَ هَشِيمًا تَذْرُوهُ الرِّيَاحُ وَكَانَ اللَّهُ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ مُقْتَدِرًا</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Jamaah\r\nJum\'ah Rahimakumullâh<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Marilah kita selalu bertakwa kepada\r\nAllah dengan arti yang seluas-luasnya, agar kita memper-oleh apa yang telah\r\ndijanjikan kepada kita:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">وَمَنْ\r\nيَتَّقِ اللَّهَ يُكَفِّرْ عَنْهُ سَيِّئَاتِهِ وَيُعَظِمْ لَهُ أَجْرًا [الطلاق: ٥]</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">\"Dan\r\nbarangsiapa yang bertakwa kepada Allah, niscaya Dia akan menutupi\r\nkesalahan-kesalahannya dan akan melipatgandakan pahala baginya.\" (QS.\r\nAth-Thalâq Ayat: 5)</span></i><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Jamaah\r\nJum\'ah Rahimakumullâh</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Al-Hayatid Dun-yâ (kehidupan dunia) memang sangat indah,\r\nselalu tampil sangat menarik, bergaya yang mempesona, sehingga akan\r\ntergila-gila orang-orang yang berambisi, akan tertipu orang-orang yang tidak\r\nberiman yang kuat, dan akan tenggelam orang-orang yang tidak mengendarai perahu\r\ntakwallâh. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Oleh karenanya Allah selalu mem-berikan\r\nperingatan kepada kita:</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">فَلَا\r\nتَغُرَّنَّكُمُ الْحَيَوةُ الدُّنْيَا [الفاطر: ٥ لقمان: </span></b><b><span lang=\"FA\">۳۳</span></b><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;\">]</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">\"Jangan\r\nsekali-kali kamu sekalian tertipu kehi-dupan dunia.\" (QS. Fâthir [35]: 5\r\ndan QS. Luqmân [31]: 33)<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">وَمَا\r\nالْحَيُوةُ الدُّنْيَا إِلَّا مَتَاعُ الْغُرُورِ [الحديد: ٢٠]</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">\"Kehidupan\r\ndunia itu bukan apa-apa kecuali hanya kesenangan yang sangat menipu.\" (QS.\r\nAli \'Imrân [3]: 185 dan QS. Al-Hadid </span></i><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Ayat</span></i><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">: 20)<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Boleh\r\nkita mencari Hayâtid Dun-yâ untuk suatu kebutuhan bukan suatu tujuan. Artinya\r\nmencari dunia sebagai bekal ibadah kepada Allah dan alat untuk mencapai\r\nkebahagiaan di akhirat nanti, bukan untuk ditumpuk-tumpuk dan digudangi untuk\r\nkebahagiaan di dunia yang fana\' ini.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Rasulullah\r\nbersabda:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">«</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">إِنَّ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">اللَّهَ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">لَمْ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">يَخْلُقُ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">خَلْقًا</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\">