quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">تَبِعْتَهُ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">فَرَّ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">مِنْكَ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>.\"</span><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">\"Sungguh\r\ndunia itu laksana bayang-bayang. Bila engkau lari darinya maka ia akan\r\nmengikutimu. Dan bila engkau mengikutinya, maka ia akan lari\r\nmeninggalkanmu.\"<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Lebih-lebih Allah telah berjanji:</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">وَمَنْ\r\nيَتَّقِ اللَّهَ يَجْعَلْ لَهُ مَخْرَجًا * وَيَرْزُقْهُ مِنْ حَيْثُ لا يَحْتَسِبُ\r\n[الطلاق: ٢-٣].</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">\"Barangsiapa yang bertakwa kepada Allah, maka Allah\r\nakan memberikan kepadanya jalan keluar dan akan memberikan rezeki kepadanya di\r\nluar perhitungan dan tanpa diduga-duga sebelumnya.\" (QS. at-Thalâq Ayat:\r\n2-3)<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Jamaah Jum\'ah Rahimakumullâh<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Mudah-mudahan kita selalu mendapatkan hidayah dan taufiq\r\n(petunjuk dan pertolongan) dari Allah sehingga kita mampu mengutamakan iman dan\r\ntakwa, beramal shaleh,bertawakkal kepada Allah dan zuhud daripada kita\r\nmenumpuk-numpuk harta dan bergelimang kemewahan, agar kita memperoleh\r\nkebahagiaan di sisi Allah, Amin..Amin...Ya Rabbal \'Alamîn.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">أَعُوْذُ\r\nبِاللَّهِ مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ الرَّحِيمِ، وَمَنْ كَانَ يُرِيدُ حَرْثَ الْآخِرَةِ نَزِدْ\r\nلَهُ فِي حَرْثِهِ ۚ وَمَنْ كَانَ يُرِيدُ حَرْثَ الدُّنْيَا نُؤْتِهِ مِنْهَا وَمَا\r\nلَهُ فِي الْآخِرَةِ مِنْ نَصِيب .</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">بَارَكَ\r\nاللَّهُ لِي وَلَكُمْ فِي الْقُرْآنِ الْعَظِيمِ، وَنَفَعَنِي وَإِيَّاكُمْ بِمَا فِيْهِ\r\nمِنَ الْآيَاتِ وَالذِّكْرِ الْحَكِيمِ، وَتَقَبَّلَ مِنِّي وَمِنْكُمْ تِلَاوَتَهُ،\r\nإِنَّهُ هُوَ السَّمِيعُ الْعَلِيمُ</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '2025-07-30 14:26:32', '2025-07-30 14:26:32');
INSERT INTO `khutbahs` (`id`, `judul`, `slug`, `image`, `desc`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(6, 'SABAR DAN SYUKUR', 'sabar-dan-syukur', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase\">الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ أَهْلِ الْحَمْدِ وَالثَّنَاءِ الْمُنْفَرِدِ\r\nبِرِدَاءِ الكبرياء الْمُتَوَحِدِ بِصِفَاتِ الْمَجْدِ وَالْعُلَاءِ، أَشْهَدُ أن لا\r\nإله إلا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ، الْمُؤَيِّدُ صَفْوَةَ الأَوْلِيَاء بِقُوَّةِ\r\nالصَّبْرِ عَلَى السَّرَّاءِ وَالضَّرَّاء وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ\r\nالْمُؤَيَّدُ بِالشَّكْرِ وَالصَّبْرِ عَلَى النَّعْمَاءِ وَالْبَلاءِ اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ\r\nعَلَى سَيِّدِنَا مُحَمَّدٍ سَيِّدِ الْأَنْبِيَاءِ، وَعَلَى أَصْحَابِهِ سَادَةِ الأَصْفِيَاءِ،\r\nوَعَلَى آلِهِ قَادَةِ الْبَرَرَةِ الْأَتْقِيَاءِ، صَلَاةَ مَحْرُوسَةً بِالدَّوَامِ\r\nعَلَى الْفَنَاءِ، وَمَصُونَةٌ بِالتَّعَاقُبِ عَنِ التَّصَرُّمِ وَالْإِنْقِضَاءِ،\r\nوَسَلَّمْ تَسْلِيمًا كَثِيرًا.</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;text-transform:uppercase;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase\">أَمَّا بَعْدُ، فَيَا أَيُّهَا الْمُسْلِمُوْنَ، أَتَّقُوا\r\nاللَّهَ حَقَّ تُقَاتِهِ وَلَا تَمُوتُنَّ إِلَّا وَأَنْتُمْ مُسْلِمُوْنَ. قَالَ تَعَالَى\r\nوَلَنَجْزِيَنَّ الَّذِيْنَ صَبَرُوا أَجْرَهُمْ بِأَحْسَنِ مَا كَانُوا يَعْمَلُونَ.\r\nوَقَالَ تَعَالَى: ﴿إِنَّمَا يُوَفِّى الصَّابِرُوْنَ أَجْرَهُمْ بِغَيْرِ حِسَابٍ.\r\nوَقَالَ النَّبِيُّ ﷺ: الصَّبْرُ نِصْفُ الإِيْمَانِ». وَقَالَ : الصَّبْرُ كَنرٌ مِنْ\r\nكُنُوزِ الْجَنَّةِ»</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;text-transform:uppercase\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase\">sidang Jum\'ah rahimakumullah</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Marilah kita bertakwa kepada Allah dan selalu meningkatkan\r\nketakwaan kita kepada-Nya. Takwa yang tidak hanya diucapkan, tetapi takwa yang\r\ndu benar-benar berdampak positif dalam akhlak budi dan semua perbuatan,\r\nlebih-lebih dalam peningka tan kesabaran dan kesyukuran kepada Allah.</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase;mso-ansi-language:IN\">jama’ah </span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase\">Jum\'ah</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase;mso-ansi-language:IN\"> </span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase\">rahimakumullah<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; iman\r\nmempunyai dua kandungan yang pokok dan prinsip, ialah sabar dan syukur.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Nabi Muhammad bersabda:</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">الإِيمَانُ\r\nنِصْفَانِ، نِصْفٌ صَبْرٌ وَنِصْفٌ شُكْرٌ</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span>&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">(رواه\r\nابو منصور الديلمي</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>(</span></b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">\"iman\r\nitu dua bagian, bagian pertama adalah sabar dan bagian kedua adalah\r\nsyukur.\"<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">(HR.\r\nAbu Manshur ad-Dilami)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Memang\r\napa yang diberikan Allah kepada manusia di dunia ini hanya dua hal: <i>an-Ni\'mah\r\nwal Baliyyah</i> (kenikmatan dan ujian). Dengan kenikmatan manusia harus\r\nbersyukur, dan dengan adanya ujian manusia harus bersabar, yang kedua-duanya\r\nitu merupakan Qadla\' (kepastian atau ketentuan dari Allah) yang manusia harus\r\nridla dalam hati yang sangat dalam. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Apabila\r\nmanusia dapat melakukan tiga hal tersebut, baru disebut beriman secara haqîqî.\r\nSeperti yang dikatakan Sahabat Ibnu Abbas:</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">لَمَّا\r\nدَخَلَ رَسُولُ الله ﷺ عَلَى الْأَنْصَارِ، فَقَالَ: «أَمُؤْمِنُوْنَ أَنْتُمْ؟» فَسَكَتُوْا</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">pada\r\nwaktu Rasulullah datang kepada sahabat Anshar, beliau bertanya: <i>\"Adakah\r\nkamu sekalian beriman?\"</i></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span>، فَقَالَ عُمَرُ : نَعَمْ يا رسول الله.<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">kemudian\r\nUmar menjawab: <i>\"Ya, wahai Rasulullah.\"</i></span><b><i><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></i></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">&nbsp;قال: «وَمَا عَلامَة ايْمَانِكُمْ؟»<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Rasulullah\r\nbersabda: <i>\"Apakah tanda-tanda iman kalian?\"</i></span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">قَالُوا:\r\nشُكْرٌ عَلَى الرَّخَاءِ وَنَصْبِرُ عَلَى الْبَلَاءِ وَنَرْضَى بِالْقَضَاءِ، فَقَالَ:\r\nمُؤْمِنُونَ وَرَبِّ الْكَعْبَةِ». أَيْ: أَنْتُمْ مُؤْمِنُونَ وَرَبِّ الْكَعْبَةِ\r\n(رواه الطبراني)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Sahabat\r\nAnshar menjawab: \"Kami bersyukur bila memperoleh keberuntungan, kami\r\nbersabar bila menerima ujian, dan kami ridla dengan qadla\' Allah (ketentuan\r\ndari Allah).\" Kemudian Rasulullah bersabda: \"Kamu sekalian sudah\r\nberiman demi Tuhan Ka\'bah.\"</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"> (HR. ath-Thabarani).</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">dari\r\nhadist tersebut jelaslah, bagi kita, bahwa semua umat manusia ini dapat\r\nmencapai predikat iman, apabila sudah mampu bersabar dengan arti yang\r\nseluas-luasnya, dan sudah mampu bersyukur juga dengan arti yang sangat luas,\r\ndan bertambah meningkat lagi iman manusia apabila sudah sanggup menerima apa\r\nsaja yang menjadi takdir Allah dengan rela hati.</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">JAMA’AH JUM\'AH RAHIMAKUMULLAH<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Kalau kita\r\nberfikir secara jujur dan kita teliti dengan akal secara jernih, maka kita tahu\r\nbahwa kenikmatan Allah yang kita terima, baik nikmat yang alami maupun nikmat\r\ndari hasil usaha yang dilakukan oleh \'umarô\' (pemerintah) bersama-sama dengan\r\nrakyat adalah sangat besar sekali. Terbukti dengan keberhasilan pembangunan\r\nkita bangsa Indonesia selama ini, sekalipun kita tidak menutup mata, masih\r\nbanyak bangsa kita yang masih belum atau kurang beruntung, maka yang sudah\r\nberhasil maupun yang belum harus bersabar, yang sudah berhasil bersabar untuk\r\nmembantu yang belum berhasil, sedangkan yang belum berhasil bersabar menerima\r\nujian dari Allah. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Agar kedua-duanya mendapatkan pahala\r\ndan hikmah dari Allah.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">begitu\r\ndikatakan:</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">\"</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">كُلُّ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">شَيْءٍ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">مِنَ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">اللَّهُ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">لَهُ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">حِكْمَةٌ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>\"</span><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">\"Segala\r\nsesuatu dari Allah pasti ada hikmahnya.\"</span></i><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dari sisi lain, kita telah menerima\r\nnikmat nikmat Allah yang sangat banyak dan sangat agung yang kita tidak mampu\r\nuntuk menghitungnya. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Allah&nbsp;\r\ntelah berfirman:</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">وَإِنْ\r\nتَعُدُّوا نِعْمَةَ اللَّهِ لَا تُحْصُوهَا [النحل: ١٨]</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">“</span></i><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Apabila\r\nkamu sekalian menghitung nikmat Allah, niscaya kamu sekalian tidak mampu untuk\r\nmenghitungnya.\"</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"> (QS. An-Nahl </span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">ayat </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">: 18)</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Maka\r\nkita harus dapat mensyukuri kenikmatan Allah dengan arti yang sangat luas.\r\nArtinya, kita dapat menerima nikmat Allah itu dengan rela hati, kemudian kita\r\nmerasa cinta (senang) kepada Allah yang memberikan nikmat itu kepada kita.\r\nSehingga kita dapat meningkatkan ibadah kita kepada Allah. </span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Selanjutnya kita dapat menggunakan nikmat itu untuk apa\r\nsaja yang diridiai Allah, yang hakikatnya mensyukuri nikmat itu akan menambah\r\npeningkatan kenikmatan Allah kepada kita, &nbsp;sebagaimana firman Allah:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">لَئِن\r\nشَكَرْتُمْ لَأَزِيدَنَّكُمْ ۖ وَلَئِن كَفَرْتُمْ إِنَّ عَذَابِي لَشَدِيدٌ﴾</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span>[ إبراهيم: 7]</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">\"Sesungguhnya jika kamu bersyukur, pasti Kami akan\r\nmenambah (nikmat) kepadamu, dan jika kamu mengingkari (nikmat-Ku), maka\r\nsesungguhnya azab-Ku sangat pedih\".</span></i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp; [Surat Ibrahim\r\nayat: 7]<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase;mso-ansi-language:IN\">Ma\'asyiral hadirin Jum\'ah RAHIMAKUMULLAH<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Apa yang\r\nterjadi di negara kita (hal-hal yang negatif) seperti: kerusuhan, kekerasan,\r\nkebrutalan, perusakan, dan sampai kepada pembunuhan, itu adalah berasal dari\r\nkurangnya kesabaran dan kesyukuran dari bangsa kita sendiri. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Kurang\r\nsabar menimbulkan kebencian, kedendaman, dan kenekatan. Dan kurang syukur\r\nmenimbulkan keangkuhan, kesombongan, dan ketidakadilan.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Oleh karenanya marilah kita saling:</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">تَوَاصَوْا\r\nبِالْحَقِّ وَتَوَاصَوْا بِالصَّبْرِ [العصر: ٣]</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">“</span></i><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Saling mengingatkan akan kebenaran dan\r\nsaling mengingatkan akan kesabaran\".</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">(QS. Al-\'Ashr ayat: 3)</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">تَعَاوَنُوا\r\nعَلَى الْبِرِّ وَالتَّقْوَى وَلَا تَعَاوَنُوا عَلَى الْإِثْمِ وَالْعُدْوَانِ﴾ [المائدة:\r\n٢]</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">\"Tolong-menolonglah\r\nkamu sekalian untuk kebaikan dan ketakwaan dan janganlah kamu sekalian\r\ntolong-menolong untuk perilaku dosa dan kejahatan\".</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"> (QS.\r\nAl-Maidah ayat:2)</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Janganlah kita saling menuduh,\r\nmenuding, dan mempersalahkan, karena hal itu akan menimbulkan situasi yang\r\ngelap, keruh, dan panas yang membara. Akan tetapi marilah kita saling merasa\r\nmemiliki kekurangan, kelemahan, dan kesalahan, Dengan demikian Insya Allah akan\r\nkita rasakan adanya situasi yang manis, aris, harmonis, dan tenang tentram,\r\ndamai, serta aman, bahagia, dan sejahtera dalam hidup dan kehidupan kita\r\nsehari-hari.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase;mso-ansi-language:IN\">Sidang Jum\'ah Rahimakumullah <o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ntext-transform:uppercase;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Marilah\r\nkita selalu memohon kepada Allah agar kita dapat bersyukur apabila memperoleh\r\nnikmat Allah, dan mampu bersabar apabila menerima bala\' (ujian) Allah, dan\r\nselalu ridla apabila mendapatkan gadia\' (ketentuan) Allah. Barangsiapa yang\r\nmampu melakukan itu semua, niscaya akan memperoleh janji-janji dari Allab, akan\r\ndiberi kehormatan yang agung, kasih sayang, dan petunjuk dari Allah ke jalan\r\nyang benar. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Sebagaimana firman Allah SWT:</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">أُولئِكَ\r\nعَلَيْهِمْ صَلَوَاتٌ مِنْ رَبِّهِمْ وَرَحْمَةٌ وَأُولئِكَ هُمُ الْمُهْتَدُونَ﴾</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span>&nbsp;[البقرة:\r\n١٥٧]</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">\"Mereka akan mendapatkan\r\npenghormatan yang agung dari Tuhan mereka dan kasih sayang, Dan mereka adalah\r\norang-orang yang mendapatkan petunjuk.\" (QS. Al-Baqarah Ayat:157)</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:\r\n150%;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">أَعُوذُ\r\nبِاللَّهِ مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ الرَّحِيمِ، [وَمَنْ عَمِلَ صَالِحًا فَلِنَفْسِهِ وَمَنْ\r\nأَسَاءَ فَعَلَيْهَا وَمَا رَبُّكَ بِظلامِ لِلْعَبِيدِ]</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:\r\n150%;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;\">بَارَكَ\r\nاللَّهُ لِي وَلَكُمْ فِي الْقُرْآنِ الْعَظِيمِ، وَنفَعَنِي وَإِيَّاكُمْ بِمَا فِيهِ\r\nمِنَ الْآيَاتِ وَالذِّكْرِ الْحَكِيمِ، وَتَقَبَّلَ مِنِّي وَمِنْكُمْ تِلاوَتَهُ،\r\nإِنَّهُ هُوَ السَّمِيعُ الْعَلِيمُ</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '2025-07-30 14:27:46', '2025-07-30 14:27:46');
INSERT INTO `khutbahs` (`id`, `judul`, `slug`, `image`, `desc`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(7, 'SHOLAT SEBAGAI TIANG AGAMA', 'sholat-sebagai-tiang-agama', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي فَرَّضَ الصَّلَاةَ عَلَى عِبَادِهِ\r\nالْمُؤْمِنِينَ، وَجَعَلَهَا عِمَادًا لِهَذَا الدِّينِ، أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لا إِلَهَ إِلَّا\r\nاللهُ وَحْدَهُ لاَ شَرِيكَ لَهُ، شَهَادَةً تُنْحِي قَائِلَهَا مِنَ الدُّخُولِ فِي\r\nزُمْرَةِ الْهَالِكِينَ، وَأَشْهَدُ أَنْ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ، سَيِّدُ\r\nالْأَنْبِيَاءِ وَالْمُرْسَلِينَ، اللَّهُمَّ فَصَلِّ عَلَى سَيِّدِنَا مُحَمَّدٍ ،\r\nوَعَلَى آلِهِ وَأَصْحَابِهِ وَالتَّابِعِينَ، وَتَابِعِيْهِمْ إِلَى يَوْمِ الدِّينِ،\r\nوَسَلَّمْ تَسْلِيمًا كَثِيرًا</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>.<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">أَمَّا بَعْدُ؛ فَيَا أَيُّهَا الْمُسْلِمُوْنَ، أَوْصِيْكُمْ\r\nوَإِيَّايَ بِتَقْوَى اللَّهِ، وَلَا تَمُوتُنَّ إِلَّا وَأَنْتُمْ مُسْلِمُوْنَ. قَالَ\r\nتَعَالَى فِي كِتَابِهِ الْكَرِيمِ: </span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>)</span></b><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">سُبْحَانَ الَّذِي أَسْرَى بِعَبْدِهِ لَيْلاً مِنَ الْمَسْجِدِ\r\nالْحَرَامِ إِلَى الْمَسْجِدِ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span> </span></b><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">الْأَقْصَى الَّذِي بَارَكْنَا حَوْلَهُ لِنُرِيَهُ مِنْ آيَاتِنَا\r\nإِنَّهُ هُوَ السَّمِيعُ البَصِيرُ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>(</span></b><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span>.</span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/roziqin/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/INetCache/IE/PP9ZY3ZT/buku_khutbah_vol.1.rtf%5b1%5d.doc#_ftn1\" name=\"_ftnref1\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"><!--[if !supportFootnotes]--><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">[1]</span></span><!--[endif]--></span></span></span></a><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"> </span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">MA’ASYIRAL HADIRIN JAMA’AH JUM’AT RAHIMAKUMULLAH<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-indent:42.55pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Marilah kita selalu bertakwa kepada Allah swt, takwa yang\r\nmendalam dan betul-betul dihayati, sehingga seolah tingkah kita selalu\r\ndikontrol oleh kadar ketakwaan kita. Manusia yang gerak-geriknya diawasi oleh\r\nrasa takwa, Ia akan memiliki pribadi tangguh, dan jiwa yang mulia, serta budi\r\npekerti yang luhur.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n42.55pt;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">MA’ASYIRAL HADIRIN JAMA’AH JUM’AT RAHIMAKUMULLAH<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-indent:42.55pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Apa sebabnya dunia semkain memburuk?. Apa sebabnya dunia\r\nsemkain kacau?. Apa sebabnya harapan-harapan baik suka menjelma menjadi\r\nkenyataan?. Aliran-aliran orang tua, aliran-aliran kuno menjawab: bahwa yang\r\nmenjadi penyebabnya adalah karena dunia semakin tua dan semakin pikun. Penyait\r\npikun itulah yang mengakitbakan dunia menjadi lupa-lupa ingat, sesaat lupa,\r\nsesaat ingat.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Sehingga zaman sekarang disebut zaman <i>edan</i>, <i>Sopo\r\nOra Edan Ora kaduman,</i> kalau tidak mengobyek tidak <i>kaduman,</i> kemudiaan\r\nkepercayaan ini diakhiri dengan kalimat yang baik “<i>Sak Bejo-bejone Kang\r\nLali, Isih Bejo Kang Iling Lan Waspodo”</i>. Beruntunglah orang orang yang\r\nsadar dan waspada, Ramalan pujangga agung ini sudah berakar kuat, sudah\r\nmendarah daging, menjadi kepercayaan orang awam yang sulit untuk dihilangkan\r\ndan sangat sulit untuk dirubah.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Sekarang bagaimana agama islam menjawab? Kita bisa\r\nmenjawab dengan tegas, “Zaman akan semakin tidak teratur kalau\r\nmanusia-manusianya meninggalkan sembahyang. Zaman akan semakin kalut, kalau\r\nmanusia-manusianya tidak mau sujud.Sebab apa kita sebagai manusia ini\r\ndiperintahkan oleh Allah swt untuk melakukan sholat?.Padahal Allah swt tidak\r\nmengambil keuntungan sama sekali dari ibadah sholatnya manusia. Sehingga semua\r\nmanusia tanpa kecuali melakukan ibadah sholat, sama sekali tidak akan menambah\r\nkeagungan Allah, tidak akan menambah kebesaran Allah, dan tidak akan menambah\r\nkekuasaan Allah. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Sebaliknya, seandainya semua manusia tanpa terkecuali\r\nmeninggalkan sholat, sama sekali tidak akan mengurangi kebesaran, kekuasaan,\r\nkeagungan Allah. Akan tetapi karena kasih sayang Allah swt kepada manusia, maka\r\nkita sebagai manusia diberi tuntunan-tuntunan hidup untuk memecahkan\r\nmasalah-masalah kita.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Kenapa justru ibadah sholat yang menjadi jawabnya? Sebab\r\nsholat itu dapat mencegah hal-hal yang kurang baik, hal-hal yang tidak baik,\r\nbahkan hal-hal yang disebut pelanggaran, sampai hal-hal yang tergolong\r\nkejahatan, Semua perbuatan yang tidak baik disebut pelanggaran, dan yang\r\ntergolong kejahatan, itu akan terbasmi bersih dan akan hilang musnah dengan\r\nibadah shola. Itulah kadar hikmah sholat atau nilai-nilai yang terkandung\r\ndidalam sholat yang difirmankan Allah swt:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n42.55pt;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">)</span></b><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">إن الصَّلوةَ تَنْهَى عَنِ الْفَحْشَاءِ وَالْمُنْكَرِ) [العنكبوت:٤٥</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>[<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">“Sesungguhnya sholat itu dapat mencegah dari\r\nperbuatan-perbuatan keji dan mungkar.” (QS. Al-‘Ankabut ayat: 45)<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Dengan dasar ayat ini, bila ada orang yang melakukan\r\nsholat tetapi tidak meninggalkan perbuatan yang keji dan mungkar, lebih-lebih\r\npelanggaran dan kejahatan, berarti ibadah sholatnya masih belum dapat\r\nmembuahkan apa-apa, belum dapat menimbulkan faedah dan hikmah apa-apa. Hal ini\r\ndiperkuat oleh hadist rasulullah yang diriwayatkan sahabat imran bin husain\r\ndengan ibnu abbas:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">»</span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">مَنْ لَمْ تَنْهَهُ صَلَاتُهُ عَنِ الْفَحْشَاءِ وَالْمُنْكَرِ\r\nلَمْ</span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span> </span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">يَزْدَدْ مِنَ اللَّهِ إِلَّا بُعْدًا».</span><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span>&nbsp;(رواه علي ابن معبد</span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>(<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">“Barang siapa yang sholatnya tidak mampu mencegah dari\r\nperbuatan yang keji-keji dan yang mungkar, maka sholatnya itu justru akan\r\ntambah menjauhkan dirinya kepada Allah swt.” (HR. Ali bin ma’bad)<a href=\"file:///C:/Users/roziqin/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/INetCache/IE/PP9ZY3ZT/buku_khutbah_vol.1.rtf%5b1%5d.doc#_ftn2\" name=\"_ftnref2\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><!--[if !supportFootnotes]--><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">[2]</span></b></span><!--[endif]--></span></a><o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n42.55pt;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n42.55pt;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">MA’ASYIRAL HADIRIN JAMA’AH JUM’AT RAHIMAKUMULLAH<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-align:center;\r\ntext-indent:42.55pt;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Ditinjau dari segi apapun, ibadah sholat mengandung makna\r\ndan nilai serta tujuan yang luhur. Baik untuk kesejahteraan rohani maupun\r\njasmani.Dokter romli dalam bukunya yang khusus menerangkan firman Allah swt:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-right:-42.55pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-indent:42.55pt;line-height:150%;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">إنَّ الصَّلوةَ تَنْهَى عَنِ الْفَحْشَاءِ وَالْمُنْكَرِ</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n42.55pt;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Beliau mengatakan “Sesungguhnya sholat itu dapat mencegah\r\nmnusia dari kejahatan dan kemungkaran.” <o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Kejahatan dan kemungkaran adalah menjadi sumber segala\r\nkekacauan dan kebinasaan. Untuk mencegah itu semua, manusia harus sholat,\r\nsembahyang, berbakti kepada Allah swt, Karena hakikat sholat itu adalah\r\npengabdian dan penyerahan jiwa dan raga kepada Allah swt, sesuai sumpah yang\r\nsenantiasa diikrarkan dalam doa iftitah.”<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-right:-42.55pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-indent:42.55pt;line-height:150%;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">إِنَّ صَلَاتِي وَنُسُكِي وَمَحْيَايَ وَمَمَاتِي لِلَّهِ رَبِّ\r\nالْعَالَمِينَ [الأنعام: ١٦٢</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>[</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-right:-42.55pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-indent:42.55pt;line-height:150%;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">“Sesungguhnya sholatku, ibadahku, hidupku, dan matiku\r\nhanyalah untuk Allah swt, tuhan semesta alam.” </span></i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">(QS. Al-An’am ayat: 126)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Kalau setiap orang mau melakukan sholat dengan tekun dan <i>khusyu’</i>,\r\njuga tunduk dan patuh kepada semua perintah Allah swt, <i>insya Allah</i> akan\r\nterciptalah kesegaran dunia ini dalam merindukan kedamaian, kesejahteraan, dan\r\nkebahagiaan yang selalu dinanti-nantikan dan diidam-idamkan. Sembahyang adalah\r\nsangat penting didalam agama islam, sebab sembahyang adalah merupakan daya\r\npenggerak untuk berbuat baik, untuk memakmurkan dunia dan untuk memberi\r\nkesejahteraan hidup dimanapun ia berada.”<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n42.55pt;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-align:center;\r\ntext-indent:42.55pt;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">KAUM MUSLIMIN YANG\r\nDIMULIAKAN ALLAH SWT<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n42.55pt;line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Mudah-mudahan kita semua diciptakan sebagai\r\nmanusia-manusia yang tekun dan aktif didalam ibadah sholat secara <i>khusyu’, </i>dan\r\nselalu berbakti kepada Allah swt, mengerjakan semua perintah-Nya, meninggalkan\r\nsemua larangan-Nya. Dapat mewujudkan kesejahteraan dan kebahagiaan, ketentraman\r\ndan kedamaian diantara&nbsp; kita dan orang\r\nlain juga semua lingkungan kita, mulai dari dunia hingga akhirat nanti. <i>Amin\r\nYa robbal alamin.</i><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-right:-42.55pt;\r\ntext-align:center;line-height:150%;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><b><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;LPMQ Isep Misbah \\(Arabic\\)&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">بَارَكَ اللَّهُ لِي وَلَكُمْ فِي الْقُرْآنِ الْعَظِيمِ، وَنفَعَنِي\r\nوَإِيَّاكُمْ بِمَا فِيهِ مِنَ الْآيَاتِ وَالذِّكْرِ الْحَكِيمِ، وَتَقَبَّلَ مِنِّي\r\nوَمِنْكُمْ تِلاوَتَهُ، إِنَّهُ هُوَ السَّمِيعُ الْعَلِيمُ</span></b><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:IN\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>.<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:-42.55pt;text-indent:1.0cm;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><div><!--[if !supportFootnotes]--><br clear=\"all\">\r\n\r\n<hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" width=\"33%\">\r\n\r\n<!--[endif]-->\r\n\r\n<div id=\"ftn1\">\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/roziqin/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/INetCache/IE/PP9ZY3ZT/buku_khutbah_vol.1.rtf%5b1%5d.doc#_ftnref1\" name=\"_ftn1\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!--[if !supportFootnotes]--><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">[1]</span></span><!--[endif]--></span></span></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span lang=\"IN\">Qs. Al-Isra’\r\nayat:1</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"ftn2\">\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/roziqin/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/INetCache/IE/PP9ZY3ZT/buku_khutbah_vol.1.rtf%5b1%5d.doc#_ftnref2\" name=\"_ftn2\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!--[if !supportFootnotes]--><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">[2]</span></span><!--[endif]--></span></span></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span lang=\"IN\">Imam Ghazali,\r\nIhya’ ulumuddin, Vol ! (Beirut Lebanon: Dar Al-Fikr, 2002), 195</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>', '2025-07-30 14:28:39', '2025-07-30 14:28:39'),
